"https://www.5metal.com.hk/upload/product/original/167416769834.膨脹PU膠4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.5metal.com.hk%2Fupload%2Fproduct%2Foriginal%2F167416769834.%E8%86%A8%E8%84%B9PU%E8%86%A04.jpg&h=b5e0d294&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.5metal.com.hk/editor_upload_image/images/膨脹PU膠3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.5metal.com.hk%2Feditor_upload_image%2Fimages%2F%E8%86%A8%E8%84%B9PU%E8%86%A03.jpg&h=1843ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/i2/720462376/O1CN01aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_!!720462376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fi2%2F720462376%2FO1CN01aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_%21%21720462376.jpg&h=e5626c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膨脹PU膠描述 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">TYL-泡沫S被修改單組分聚氨酯泡沫填充或接縫和間隙密封</span>。泡沫噴出後迅速膨脹並迅速與空氣中的水分反應固化成精細的蜂窩結構泡沫。它<span style=\"color: red;\">形成了一個強有力的鍵合最建築材料</span>，如混凝土表面上。 TYL-泡沫S被在噴嘴增壓級氣霧罐供應。<br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠用途 :<br />\n‧腔填充 <br />\n‧在車頂結構的所有開口密封 <br />\n‧聲學障板的應用 <br />\n‧吸音層的應用 <br />\n‧安裝窗戶和門框 <br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠優點 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧高灌裝能力 </span><br />\n‧高絕緣值，熱學和聲學 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧很好的粘結性能 <br />\n‧卓越的穩定性不收縮或膨脹後 </span><br />\n‧無氟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>復活彩蛋</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bZyV8M4.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"2cafa152b0e8b594d54c7021839a9b286dbb793a","tid":1650022,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"《人手轉載》<br />\n<br />\n希望大家維持嗌五大訴求：<br />\n1.缺一不可本來就有環環相扣既意思，正如林鄭撤回咗條例，都唔會改嗌四大訴求，簡單啲講，呢句野既結果一係5，一係0，冇其他。<br />\n2.解散警隊呢個訴求並唔夠實際同具體，基本上五大訴求達成就已經可以蓋括埋解散警隊既效果，正如一開始第五個訴求係林鄭下台，大家都覺得呢個訴求唔實際，所以改做雙普選，所以，我地係唔需要特登加多一個訴求落去，咁先比到人睇我地一直爭取緊既係具體、可行、實際既訴求。<br />\n解散警隊可以獨立嗌，代表我地對警隊嚴重不滿，但唔好將佢當做第六大訴求。<br />\n3.國際啱啱先開始知到我地爭取緊既係五大訴求而唔係林鄭一句撤回就咁簡單，所以維持五大訴求先比到人一種由始此終都係爭取緊同一樣野既觀感。"},{"pid":"24fa9ec0998902cab6266da67759584b94f861f2","tid":1650022,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:42:40.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71rUgoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71rUgoF.jpg&h=dfc19a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmG1FQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmG1FQk.jpg&h=16c44ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jk7sBoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJk7sBoG.png&h=6f2b4d34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oue6RW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOue6RW2.jpg&h=f95c8cc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea5584df0b37ff47df5e0172bcef96e3d02e52d3","tid":1650022,"uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:51:27.000Z","msg":"推！！<br />\n大家落力推其他post！！<br />\n唔好比生日事件覆蓋成個台！！<br />\n！！！！！"},{"pid":"5bfaa3094b6deb02ed47861fb3f32e1e54ee16f0","tid":1650022,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b12b1717fb99d34d4d194e34e3961bd1b6c10b39","tid":1650022,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}